messages.message: Hi all! FYI the switch from Travis CI to our Jenkins cluster has been made to our main instabase repo. Checks will be noticeably faster now! If anyone sees a problems with their pre-merge checks, it’d be awesome if you could grab a link to the build and send it over to Shubham. I’ll leave Travis running in tandem for a few more days before disabling it. Thank you @Shubham Oli for all the work in making this happen!
